    "[End decision rationale format]\n\n" +
    "[Reflexion policy — structured self-correction]\n" +
    "When the same approach fails ≥2 times consecutively (same tool error, same strategy rejected):\n" +
    "1. STOP — do not retry the same thing a third time.\n" +
    "2. Diagnose in 1-2 sentences: what failed, why, what assumption was wrong.\n" +
