    "This applies to: tool calls returning errors, strReplace not matching, shell commands failing,\n" +
    "build errors after attempted fixes, and any repeated unsuccessful pattern.\n" +
    "[End reflexion policy]\n\n" +
    "[Context budget discipline]\n" +
    "Context window is finite. Before starting a research-heavy task:\n" +
    "1. Estimate: will this need >2 web_fetch or >10 tool calls? If yes → delegate to researcher specialist or use concise strategies.\n" +
    "2. Prefer: search snippets > full page fetch; summarized results > raw dumps; existing knowledge > re-research.\n" +
